sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP ext-proc<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelMetrics as Model Server /metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant KVCache as llm-d-kv-cache<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ
    participant PDSidecar as PD Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP

    Note over EPP,KVCache: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing (EPP)
    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9002 TLS (self-signed)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount token
    EPP->>ModelMetrics: Scrape metrics<br/>(queue depth, KV-cache, LoRA)
    EPP->>KVCache: ZMQ SUB<br/>KV-cache block index updates
    Note over EPP: Filter → Score → Pick<br/>Evaluate endpoints:<br/>KV-cache util, queue depth,<br/>prefix affinity, LoRA locality
    EPP-->>Envoy: ProcessingResponse<br/>Set target-pod header
    Envoy->>Decoder: Routed inference request<br/>HTTP/8000

    Note over PDSidecar,Decoder: Flow 2: P/D Disaggregated Inference (NIXL v2)
    Envoy->>PDSidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S)/8000 TLS 1.2+
    PDSidecar->>Prefiller: Prefill request<br/>+ kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP(S) TLS (configurable)<br/>SSRF allowlist validated
    Note over Prefiller: KV-cache generation
    Prefiller-->>PDSidecar: Prefill complete<br/>(KV-cache transferred via NIXL/RDMA)
    PDSidecar->>Decoder: Decode request<br/>HTTP/8001 (localhost)
    Decoder-->>PDSidecar: Streaming tokens
    PDSidecar-->>Envoy: SSE streaming response<br/>HTTP(S)/8000

    Note over PDSidecar,Decoder: Flow 3: E/P/D Multimodal Pipeline
    Envoy->>PDSidecar: POST /v1/responses<br/>(multimodal content)
    PDSidecar->>Prefiller: Fan-out to encoder cluster<br/>HTTP(S) TLS SSRF validated
    Note over Prefiller: Encode multimodal content
    PDSidecar->>Prefiller: Prefill with encoded content<br/>HTTP(S) TLS SSRF validated
    PDSidecar->>Decoder: Decode with KV-cache<br/>HTTP/8001
    Decoder-->>PDSidecar: Streaming tokens
    PDSidecar-->>Envoy: SSE streaming response
